creator: Villatravellers
descriptionHtml:
The new app from Villatravellers makes managing your booking even simpler. Designed with you in mind, now it’s even easier to prepare for your upcoming holiday in Sicily!

Your Villa Booking
Find all details about your villa booking in the app. You can also book extras directly through the app making your holiday preparations even easier. There’s a helpful Villa Guidebook with everything you need to know about the property so you’ll feel right at home as soon as you arrive, and you can also get to know the local area with our interactive map full of the best places to visit!

Your Experience Booking
Booked an experience? Or do you want to book an extra experience? You can on the app! Everything you need to know about the experience, including meeting points, times, and much more, can be found on the app. All you need to do is enjoy the experience!

Your Time in Sicily
Villatravellers are experts on Sicily, and want to share this knowledge with you. Read up about the island with the Sicilian Handbook with helpful hints, and even pick up a bit of Italian using the phrase book! You can also create your own itinerary using the plan your trip section with the best towns, beaches, and sights to visit.

Share your Plans
It’s simple to share your travel plans with your friends! Travelling with a group, or with your family? Let everyone know all about the villa and the local area by sharing the app. You’ll all be up to date and the excitement will only grow!

Villatravellers. Here for You
During your time in Sicily you’ll have access to our local manager 24/7 via the app. You can get in touch for any assistance you might need. Rest at ease that you’re being looked after by Villatravellers!

Simple & Intuitive
Rich in detail, but easy to follow, you’ll love having the App to help manage your holiday in Sicily.

The App is available in four languages (English, Italian, German, French).
